-gold, two-silver, one-bronze tally the country netted in Tokyo for its biggest medal haul in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4695040031866686e-14, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999972844212189, \"rank\": 2.715585971342266e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Diaz, it all comes down to the athletes' desire to succeed.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is all in the heart and mindset and the discipline and grit in the things that they do every day,\\\" said Diaz.\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You need to have a dream.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": []}]}"